{"tid":2202862,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"你看不見的，就不存在嗎？","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T05:12:27.000Z","uid":347001,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32bbabed7074b76ec8d737bb448617699666c34f","tid":2202862,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"弟子問佛祖：&ldquo;您所說的極樂世界，我看不見，怎麼能夠相信呢？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n佛祖把弟子帶進一間漆黑的屋子，告訴他：&ldquo;牆角有一把錘子。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n弟子不管是瞪大眼睛，還是眯成小眼，仍然伸手不見五指，只好說我看不見。<br />\n<br />\n佛祖點燃了一支蠟燭，牆角果然有一把錘子。<br />\n<br />\n你看不見的，就不存在嗎？"},{"pid":"e06834b4d08013911cf0c912814ed4fc6f88cac7","tid":2202862,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"我佛故我在🙏🏻"},{"pid":"6c62cef20002a087bf52518a9922e30536597677","tid":2202862,"uid":347001,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e06834b4d08013911cf0c912814ed4fc6f88cac7","tid":2202862,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"我佛故我在🙏🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2be8beef6ea2e018b0525c50f566a5614228e4","tid":2202862,"uid":347001,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32bbabed7074b76ec8d737bb448617699666c34f","tid":2202862,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"弟子問佛祖：&ldquo;您所說的極樂世界，我看不見，怎麼能夠相信呢？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n佛祖把弟子帶進一間漆黑的屋子，告訴他：&ldquo;牆角有一把錘子。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n弟子不管是瞪大眼睛，還是眯成小眼，仍然伸手不見五指，只好說我看不見。<br />\n<br />\n佛祖點燃了一支蠟燭，牆角果然有一把錘子。<br />\n<br />\n你看不見的，就不存在嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:03:56.000Z","msg":"肉眼能看到多少"},{"pid":"a56803c5976ac5cc20309fc145c46ebdf135b938","tid":2202862,"uid":354471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bXowdZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn